<!-- ABOUT SECTION-->
    <div class="about-section">About Us</div>

    <p class="para2">Established in 2008 as Star Enterprises, VDM Technologies is a trusted supplier of office equipment and IT solutions.<br>
        We are the authorized channel partner for top brands like Samsung, Toshiba, Hitachi, Lenovo, and more.<br>
        Over the years, we’ve built a strong presence among government offices, educational institutions, and corporate sectors.<br>
        Our offerings include laptops, desktops, printers, copiers, projectors, CCTVs, networking devices, and genuine spare parts.<br>
        We also provide reliable maintenance and support services to ensure smooth operation of your digital infrastructure.<br>
        Driven by our motto — “Customer-first, technology-driven” — we combine quality products with dedicated service to deliver smart, future-ready solutions.
    </p>
    <img src="about.webp" class="aboutimg2" alt="about" data-aos="zoom-out">

